      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
        <h3>Front-Load Washers (FF/AFN series)</h3>
        <p class="model-list">AFN50RSP · AFNE9BSP · AFN51FSP · AFNE9BJP</p>
        <p>Higher-capacity front-load variants. Door latch and drain pump the common service items. Speed Queen's heavier-duty door boot rubber outlasts consumer-tier brands by 3-5 years on the same compound stress test.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
        <h3>Electric Dryers (ADE series)</h3>
        <p class="model-list">ADE4BRGS173TW01 · ADE5BRGS173TW01 · ADE3SRGS173TW01</p>
        <p>Electric dryer line matched to AWN top-load and AFN front-load washers. Thermal fuse + vent inspection the most common service. Heating element year 8-12, drum belt year 7-10.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
        <h3>Gas Dryers (ADG series)</h3>
        <p class="model-list">ADG3SRGS173TW01 · ADG4BRGS173TW01 · ADG5BRGS173TW01</p>
        <p>Gas dryer line. Service items overlap electric tree plus gas valve coil and igniter year 8-12. Licensed gas work, CSLB C-20.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
        <h3>Mechanical-Control Variants</h3>
        <p class="model-list">TR3000WN · AWN432SP-base</p>
