        <p class="model-list">TR7000WN · AWN542SP · AFNE9BSP</p>
        <p>Electronic-control variants with display and cycle programmability. Add board-level diagnostic during service work; year 12-15 control-board service ($345-$525) is the trade-off for the interface convenience.</p>
      </div>
